dataList.title: La Manchaland
dataList.content: I didn't... I had no idea something could taste so delicious...!

dataList.title: La Manchaland
dataList.content: How did we even survive for so long without tasting something this delectable? How could we ever forget this sensation?
They are corroded by an Abnormality.

dataList.title: La Manchaland
dataList.content: Y-you... the blood you've spilled thus far... We followed your trail of blood...

dataList.title: La Manchaland
dataList.content: Oh... I miss it so much...

dataList.title: La Manchaland
dataList.content: The day when we had our first accident at La Manchaland...

dataList.title: La Manchaland
dataList.content: The blood dripping from one of our guests...

dataList.title: La Manchaland

dataList.content: Oh, the elation I felt then...
